<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Evelyn:
[B]I have been able to purchase the spell from the vendor in S Qeynos that carries it.  *However* - you must raise your faction from dubious to apprehensive in order to do this.

I raised my faction by doing the spell components quest.  There is an NPC outside of the towers (not all the way in the back - don't remember the name off hand), that wants 2 bat wings, 1 rat wisker, and 1 snake scale.  It is a pain in the neck to kill bats, rats, and snakes when you are level 9, but I did that.  It took 25 sets of spell components to go from dubious to aprehensive.  At apprehensive, the spell cost over 1 pp more than the listing in Casters Realm.

Or... at level 9... the run from Qeynos to Freeport is not impossible to accoomplish.  You have your SoW.  Just be careful.[/B][/QUOTE]

</TEXTAREA>
